metadata.name: Werewolf#1
metadata.description: 777 AI Monsters is a project dedicated to art, and, more specifically, our favorite classic monsters brought to life through AI.  Werewolves is our genesis collection and others will follow.  The project is set to evolve, as does its roadmap. For starters, we'll go simple and straightforward.  Holders benefits:  - A free mint from our next collection, featuring another classic monster.  - Access to raffles (Airdrops, % from secondary sales, WL from collab projects).  - Exclusive WL for a "Degen freemint" larger collection, 100% hand drawn.    It's just the beginning...Monsters are stronger together !
